Congratulations!
You successfully started your first encoding :) and this is only the beginning. The Bitmovin Encoding API is extremely flexible and allows many customizations and provides with access to the latest codecs and video streaming optimizations and technologies out there. Have a look at the
API Reference
to learn more.
